All messages begin with "error" or "done" on the first line

server
  command interpreter
    commands
      next
        restarts timer
        goes to next background
      refresh
        recalculates background and reapplies it
      var [varname [newvalue]]
        no args
          prints name-value pairs for all settable variables
        1 arg
          shows that variable, its current value, and description of it
        2 args
          sets the given arg to a new value
  action timeout
    time to wait
    randomized wait (gaussian max range)

action
  chooser
    random from directory(s)
    from ordered list
      defined in memory
      defined in file
  image processor
    process
      darken by percent
      darken to maximum brightness
    set background
      tiled
      stretched
      centered
